channel.title: RSBots
channel.description:
Does anyone have the "rsbots" client? I went to the site and another to, and i click to download the client and they both take me to like impsoft or something, and it says "you can only download once every 180 seconds" i leave it on that screen and it never downloads, so i refresh the page and yet it still doesn't download. Does anyone have a link for that same client i can download?
Thanks ~Duzzy
